member.returns:
Returns -1 if there is no matching between the glyph and the specified glyph data. In the case if match is found it returns:
0 - the glyph matches with specified glyph data as they are provided;
90, 180 or 270 - the glyph matches with specified data if they are rotated by 90, 180 or 270 degree respectively in counter clockwise direction.

Returns -1 if there is no matching between two specified glyphs. In the case if match is found it returns:
0 - the two glyphs match each other as they are provided;
90, 180 or 270 - the source glyph matches with target glyph if it is rotated by 90, 180 or 270 degree respectively in counter clockwise direction.
